There are two methods of making records unavailable in the system: One is to delete the record, the other is to de-activate the record. A de-activated record is not available for selection, but available for reports. There are two reasons for de-activating and not deleting records: (1) The system requires the record for audit purposes. (2) The record is referenced by other records. E.g., you cannot delete a Business Partner, if there are invoices for this partner record existing. You de-activate the Business Partner and prevent that this record is used for future entries.

Identifies an item which is either purchased or sold in this organization.
Identifica un artículo que puede ser comprado o vendido es esta organización.

The Delivery Rule indicates when an order should be delivered. For example should the order be delivered when the entire order is complete, when a line is complete or as the products become available.

La Regla de Entrega indica cuando una orden debe ser entregada. Por Ej. Si la orden debiera entregarse cuando está completa; cuando una partida está completa o cuando el producto llega a estar disponible.

The Credit Limit indicates the total amount allowed "on account" in primary accounting currency. If the Credit Limit is 0, no check is performed. Credit Management is based on the Total Open Amount, which includes Vendor activities.
Total pendiente del total de la factura pendiente.
El límite de crédito indica el total de deuda permitida.
Freight Categories are used to calculate the Freight for the Shipper selected
Las categorías de fletes se utilizan para calcular los fletes del expedidor seleccionado
Optional short description of the record
A description is limited to 255 characters.
Opción de una breve descripción del registro.
The Date Promised indicates the date, if any, that an Order was promised for.
Fecha de promesa de la orden.
La fecha prometida indica la fecha; si hay alguna; en que la orden fue prometida al cliente.
The Document Type determines document sequence and processing rules
El tipo de documento determina la secuencia del documento y las reglas de proceso

Credit Management is inactive if Credit Status is No Credit Check, Credit Stop or if the Credit Limit is 0. If active, the status is set automatically set to Credit Hold, if the Total Open Balance (including Vendor activities) is higher then the Credit Limit. It is set to Credit Watch, if above 90% of the Credit Limit and Credit OK otherwise.
The On Hand Quantity indicates the quantity of a product that is on hand in a warehouse.
La cantidad en existencia indica la cantidad de un producto que se encuentra en inventario
The UOM defines a unique non monetary Unit of Measure
La UM define una unidad de medida única no monetaria
Fecha/tiempo cuando se realiza la recolección

Document sequence number of the document

The document number is usually automatically generated by the system and determined by the document type of the document. If the document is not saved, the preliminary number is displayed in "<>".
If the document type of your document has no automatic document sequence defined, the field is empty if you create a new document. This is for documents which usually have an external number (like vendor invoice). If you leave the field empty, the system will generate a document number for you. The document sequence used for this fallback number is defined in the "Maintain Sequence" window with the name "DocumentNo_<TableName>", where TableName is the actual name of the table (e.g. C_Order).

The Sales Representative indicates the Sales Rep for this Region. Any Sales Rep must be a valid internal user.
El Agente comercial indica el Agente comercial para esta región.
How the order will be delivered
The Delivery Via indicates how the products should be delivered. For example, will the order be picked up or shipped.
La vía de entrega indica como el producto debería ser entregado. Por Ej. Si la orden será recogida o embarcada.
The Freight Cost Rule indicates the method used when charging for freight.
La regla de costo de flete indica el método usado para cargar los fletes.

The Order is a control document. The Order is complete when the quantity ordered is the same as the quantity shipped and invoiced. When you close an order, unshipped (backordered) quantities are cancelled.
La ID de la orden de ventas es un identificador único de la orden de ventas; Ésta es controlada por la secuencia del documento para este tipo de documento.
The Priority indicates the importance (high, medium, low) of this document
La prioridad indica la importancia (alta; media; baja) de este documento
The Warehouse identifies a unique Warehouse where products are stored or Services are provided.
El almacén identifica un punto único donde los productos son almacenados
Indicates the unique line for a document. It will also control the display order of the lines within a document.

The Movement Quantity indicates the quantity of a product that has been moved.

The name of an entity (record) is used as an default search option in addition to the search key. The name is up to 60 characters in length.

Generar Factura desde Orden de Salida
Esta búsqueda inteligente permite seleccionar las líneas de orden de salida listas para facturar.

Data.oldValue: iob.IsSOTrx = 'Y' AND iobl.Processed = 'Y' AND COALESCE(ol.QtyOrdered, 0) <> COALESCE(ol.QtyInvoiced, 0) AND (COALESCE(iobl.PickedQty, 0) - COALESCE(ol.QtyInvoiced, 0)) > 0 AND NOT EXISTS(SELECT 1 FROM C_Invoice i INNER JOIN C_InvoiceLine il ON(il.C_Invoice_ID = i.C_Invoice_ID) WHERE il.WM_InOutBoundLine_ID = iobl.WM_InOutBoundLine_ID AND i.DocStatus IN('CO', 'CL'))

PO.Data: iob.IsSOTrx = 'Y' AND iobl.Processed = 'Y' AND COALESCE(ol.QtyOrdered, 0) > COALESCE(ol.QtyInvoiced, 0) AND (COALESCE(iobl.MovementQty, 0) - COALESCE(ol.QtyInvoiced, 0)) > 0 AND NOT EXISTS(SELECT 1 FROM C_Invoice i INNER JOIN C_InvoiceLine il ON(il.C_Invoice_ID = i.C_Invoice_ID) WHERE il.WM_InOutBoundLine_ID = iobl.WM_InOutBoundLine_ID AND i.DocStatus IN('CO', 'CL'))
